    # narrador "You see [riku.n] wobble and lose his balance for a few seconds, but he recovers quickly."
    narrador "Você vê [riku.n] cambalear e perder o equilíbrio por alguns segundos, mas ele se recupera rapidamente."

# game/scripts/Events/Locations/Dressrosa/dressrosa_h11.rpy:34
translate portuguese dressrosa_h11_03027945:

    # riku "Damn... These wounds seem worse than I thought..."
    riku "Caramba... Essas feridas parecem piores do que eu imaginava..."

# game/scripts/Events/Locations/Dressrosa/dressrosa_h11.rpy:35
translate portuguese dressrosa_h11_3e03809d:

    # player "Why don't you rest a bit, man..."
    player "Por que você não descansa um pouco, cara...?"

# game/scripts/Events/Locations/Dressrosa/dressrosa_h11.rpy:36
translate portuguese dressrosa_h11_ed29b515:

    # riku "Heh... There'll be time for this old man to rest later..."
    riku "Heh... Haverá tempo para este velho descansar mais tarde..."

# game/scripts/Events/Locations/Dressrosa/dressrosa_h11.rpy:37
translate portuguese dressrosa_h11_aa349038:

    # player "You should eat a lot, that's how I usually heal my wounds"
    player "Você deveria comer bastante, geralmente é assim que eu curo meus ferimentos."

# game/scripts/Events/Locations/Dressrosa/dressrosa_h11.rpy:38
translate portuguese dressrosa_h11_333add06:

    # riku "Hahaha... I don't know what kind of medicine you trust in, but I don't think that'll work for this old body..."
    riku "Hahaha... Não sei em que tipo de remédio você confia, mas acho que isso não vai funcionar para este meu corpo velho..."

# game/scripts/Events/Locations/Dressrosa/dressrosa_h11.rpy:39
translate portuguese dressrosa_h11_5a38c2b7:

    # player "If not, I think I heard there's an infirmary in the basement, maybe they could give you a quick check-up"
    player "Caso contrário, acho que ouvi dizer que há uma enfermaria no subsolo; talvez eles possam lhe fazer um exame rápido."

# game/scripts/Events/Locations/Dressrosa/dressrosa_h11.rpy:40
translate portuguese dressrosa_h11_63969cd4:

    # riku "Mnmn... Koff... koff... The infirmary..."
    riku "Hum... Cof... cof... A enfermaria..."

# game/scripts/Events/Locations/Dressrosa/dressrosa_h11.rpy:41
translate portuguese dressrosa_h11_01ef1718:

    # riku "I should investigate a bit... But I haven't had the chance, they don't let anyone in unless they're hurt."
    riku "Eu deveria investigar um pouco... Mas ainda não tive oportunidade, eles não deixam ninguém entrar a menos que esteja ferido."

# game/scripts/Events/Locations/Dressrosa/dressrosa_h11.rpy:42
translate portuguese dressrosa_h11_e0b482f9:

    # riku "I've heard strange things from the gladiators about that place... Apparently something weird is going on there..."
    riku "Ouvi coisas estranhas dos gladiadores sobre aquele lugar... Aparentemente, algo bizarro está acontecendo lá..."

# game/scripts/Events/Locations/Dressrosa/dressrosa_h11.rpy:43
translate portuguese dressrosa_h11_c2b783ca:

    # player "Strange things?! What are you implying?"
    player "Coisas estranhas?! O que você está insinuando?"

# game/scripts/Events/Locations/Dressrosa/dressrosa_h11.rpy:44
translate portuguese dressrosa_h11_92bf307c:

    # riku "I don't know, it doesn't matter now... I was heading to the arena, someone important to me should be about to fight!"
    riku "Não sei, não importa agora... Eu estava indo para a arena, alguém importante para mim deveria estar prestes a lutar!"

# game/scripts/Events/Locations/Dressrosa/dressrosa_h11.rpy:46
translate portuguese dressrosa_h11_3cfd3a11:

    # narrador "You see [riku.n] stumble again, almost collapsing to the floor; he's gravely injured..."
    narrador "Você vê [riku.n] tropeçar novamente, quase caindo no chão; ele está gravemente ferido..."

# game/scripts/Events/Locations/Dressrosa/dressrosa_h11.rpy:47
translate portuguese dressrosa_h11_e282f5c1:

    # player "Hey hey, you'd better rest a bit in a corner... You won't last much longer..."
    player "Ei, ei, é melhor você descansar um pouco num canto... Você não vai durar muito mais..."

# game/scripts/Events/Locations/Dressrosa/dressrosa_h11.rpy:48
translate portuguese dressrosa_h11_1109ce84:

    # riku "Ufff... You might be right..."
    riku "Ufa... Você pode ter razão..."

# game/scripts/Events/Locations/Dressrosa/dressrosa_h11.rpy:50
translate portuguese dressrosa_h11_849306fd:

    # riku "..."
    riku "..."

