    # rebecca "There are many others like me who are sacrificing themselves to save [Dressrosa.n]... And to save ourselves..."
    rebecca "Existem muitos outros como eu que se sacrificam para salvar [Dressrosa.n]... E para nos salvar..."

# game/scripts/Events/Locations/Dressrosa/dressrosa_h11.rpy:117
